name: Characters of the World # 01
description:
A series of 40 characters of the world.

Sarah Gamp, the famous monthly nurse in "Martin Chuzzlewit", has obtained a world-wide celebrity: her continual references to her mythical friend "Mrs. Arris", and her no less frequent attentions to the bottle, when she was so "dispoged", are typical points in her character.


Based on "Characters from the works of Charles Dickens : a series of 40"
